e=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">SelfAuth</span>" or "NoAuth"</span></p><p style=3D=
"margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);">Convert one en=
try to multiple responses</span></p><p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;"><span=
 style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">One ent=
ry for maker (<span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);"><span style=3D"color: r=
gb(0,0,0);">approvalWorkflowAuthorisationLogDetails</span>[i].workflowReque=
stCreatedBy) </span></span>and one or multiple entries for approvers (<span=
 style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">approva=
lWorkflowAuthorisationLogDetails</span>[i].actionedBy[j])</span></span></p>=
<p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);">Ign=
ore <span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">approvalWorkflowAuthorisationLogDeta=
ils</span> entry does not contains "Approved" in <span style=3D"color: rgb(=
0,0,0);">approvalWorkflowAuthorisationLogDetails[i].workflowStatusUpdates.s=
tatus </span></span></p><p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;"><br></p><p><span =
style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">otherwise, </span></p><p style=3D"margin-left:=
 40.0px;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">One entry for maker (<span sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">approvalWor=
kflowAuthorisationLogDetails</span>[i].workflowRequestCreatedBy)</span></sp=
an></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>Only approved records should be shown in the list.&nbsp;</li>
<li>For&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">SelfAuth/</span>No Auth the=
re is no authorisation entry, just last updated/archived entry would be pre=
sent.&nbsp;</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
